text: The Sydney Roosters are an Australian professional rugby league team. The team is based in the Eastern Suburbs of Sydney, New South Wales. They were founded in 1908. They currently play in the National Rugby League competition. They have won 15 premierships, most recently in 2019. The Sydney Roosters are the only club to take part in every season of top-flight rugby league competition in Australia. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:National Rugby League Category:Sports clubs and teams in Sydney Category:1908 establishments in Australia
